---
title: Pho-Style Beef Meatball & Baby Broccoli Soup with Udon Noodles & Asian Greens
description: Be transported to the streets of Vietnam with this pho-inspired meatball soup special. Warming and bursting with flavours
from a rich brothy soup sprinkled with baby broccoli and udon noodles. Add some beef meatballs on top to finish off this
beloved bowl of pho.
